Spring mvc WEB

flow of mcv
we start our project then  web.xml  (url /) --> user controller ( url / match and then redirecting to home.jsp) 
open home.jsp( click on add user --> addUserPage -> user controller( url /addUserPage match then redirecting to user.jsp

1.create new maven project( spring-mvc)
2.we got inbuilt ( req. dependancies, web.xml ,home.jsp,mvcConfiguration(dispatcher),controller)

* spring mvc + hibernate integration
3. integrate hibernate in spring mvc
	3.1 add dependancies (  hibernate core and mysql connector)
	3.2 hibernate configuration class  (we required datasource and hibernate properties for sessionfactory)

4.	create package structure
	configuration	controller		entity		service		dao	

5.mvc architecture layers (controller > service > dao )

6.design pattern ( I to C   ..  interface to class )
	
	
	
	
